{"tid":2281534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部：立法會議員資格問題 國際戰線幫不了忙","createTime":"2020-11-11T08:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T11:11:19.000Z","uid":21470,"like":28,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"214742735963610828e173bb9e66991c56eda89f","tid":2281534,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:47:24.000Z","msg":"外交部：立法會議員資格問題 別國無權插手干預<br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人汪文斌，在北京的記者會強調，香港特區立法會議員資格問題，純屬中國的內政，別國無權說三道四，插手干預。<br />\n<br />\n汪文斌表示，全國人大常委會根據憲法、香港基本法和港區國安法的有關規定，對立法會議員資格作出決定，是堅持和完善一國兩制制度體系、落實香港基本法和香港國安法等有關規定的必然要求，也是維護香港法治和特區憲制秩序的必要之舉，合情合理、合憲合法；全國人大常委會有關決定，針對的是不符合擁護香港基本法和效忠特區法定要求和條件的立法會議員，違法者必須承擔法律責任，這是任何一個法治社會的基本准則。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2365784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2365784&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=bdf0bedc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2365784</a>"},{"pid":"2a3b47bb970423ba202dc64705df1b59a74ceb8d","tid":2281534,"uid":237425,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:48:07.000Z","msg":"即係幫到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5934806b77d22d9b52e50443c35df83c3193a036","tid":2281534,"uid":143230,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"2a3b47bb970423ba202dc64705df1b59a74ceb8d","tid":2281534,"uid":237425,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:48:07.000Z","msg":"即係幫到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:51:46.000Z","msg":"十二月立法會全體=制裁名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e914d428ca2852f882b004f953cdcdb3a46bec99","tid":2281534,"uid":266503,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5934806b77d22d9b52e50443c35df83c3193a